import React from "react";
import bannerImage from "../image/bes-bg.png"
import imageproduct1 from "../image/best-image-01.png"
import imageproduct2 from "../image/best-image-02.png"
import imageproduct3 from "../image/best-image-03.png"
import { BannerWrapper,ImageBanner,Header ,Content , ProductWrapper,ImageProduct,Box,Product,TextBox} from "./BestProductBanner.styles";
export default function BProductBanner() {
  return (
    <BannerWrapper>
      <ImageBanner src={bannerImage}></ImageBanner>
      <Header>BEST PRODUCT</Header>
      <Content>How to create mobile-optimized videos in minutes. Not a designer, 
               every team makes a lot of videos Can be trimmed. Take the first</Content>
      <ProductWrapper>
      <Product>
        <ImageProduct src={imageproduct1}></ImageProduct>
       <Box></Box>
      </Product>
      <Product>
        <ImageProduct src={imageproduct2}></ImageProduct>
       <Box></Box>
      </Product>
      <Product>
        <ImageProduct src={imageproduct2}></ImageProduct>
       <Box>
         <TextBox to create 
mobile-optimized></TextBox>
       </Box>
      </Product>
     
      
      </ProductWrapper>
      
    </BannerWrapper>
  );
}
